<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>{{.Meta.Title}}</title>
<style>
  /* ============== Page setup ============== */
  @page {
    size: A4;
    margin: 14mm 12mm 16mm 12mm;
    @bottom-center {
      content: counter(page) " / " counter(pages);
      font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    @bottom-left {
      content: "矩阵云安全平台 · K8s 容器安全专项报告";
      font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }
    @bottom-right {
      content: "机密 · 仅限内部使用";
      font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
      font-size: 9px;
      color: #dc2626;
    }
  }
  @page :first {
    margin: 0;
    @bottom-center { content: none; }
    @bottom-left { content: none; }
    @bottom-right { content: none; }
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  html, body {
    margin: 0; padding: 0;
    font-family: "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #1f2937;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
    print-color-adjust: exact;
  }

  /* ============== Cover ============== */
  .cover {
    width: 100vw;
    height: 100vh;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 28mm 22mm 24mm 22mm;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at top right, rgba(114,46,209,0.07) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at bottom left, rgba(37,99,235,0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
      #ffffff;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
    row-gap: 0;
    page-break-after: always;
    position: relative;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cover-meta { align-self: end; }
  .cover::before {
    content: ""; position: absolute; left: 0; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #2563eb 0%, #722ed1 100%);
  }
  .cover-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 18px; }
  .cover-brand img { width: 64px; height: 64px; }
  .cover-brand-name {
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600; color: #1f2937; line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }
  .cover-brand-en {
    font-size: 12px; color: #6b7280;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace; margin-top: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .cover-mid {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center; align-items: center; text-align: center;
    min-height: 0;
  }
  .cover-kind {
    font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 10px; color: #2563eb;
    font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .cover-title {
    font-size: 60px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #722ed1 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    margin: 0 0 30px 0;
  }
  .cover-period {
    font-size: 19px; color: #374151;
    padding: 10px 28px; border: 1px solid #d1d5db; border-radius: 999px;
    background: #ffffff;
  }
  .cover-deco {
    margin-top: 22px;
    width: 240px; height: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #2563eb, #722ed1, transparent);
  }

  /* 亮点四列 */
  .cover-highlights {
    margin-top: 36px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 14px;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .cover-highlights .hl {
    padding: 14px 10px;
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    border-top: 3px solid #2563eb;
    border-radius: 6px;
    background: #ffffff;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }
  .cover-highlights .hl.hl-c { border-top-color: #dc2626; }
  .cover-highlights .hl.hl-b { border-top-color: #ea580c; }
  .cover-highlights .hl.hl-p { border-top-color: #722ed1; }
  .cover-highlights .hl-num {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 26px; font-weight: 700; color: #111827;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px; line-height: 1.1;
  }
  .cover-highlights .hl-lbl {
    font-size: 11.5px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* 本期摘要 */
  .cover-summary {
    margin-top: 28px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 16px 18px;
    border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.04) 0%, transparent 100%);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }
  .cover-summary-title {
    font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; color: #2563eb;
    margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: 2px;
  }
  .cover-summary-text {
    font-size: 14px; color: #374151; line-height: 1.9;
    text-align: justify;
  }

  .cover-meta {
    border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
    padding-top: 22px;
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 10px 40px;
    font-size: 14.5px;
  }
  .cover-meta-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; }
  .cover-meta-label { color: #6b7280; }
  .cover-meta-value { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace; font-weight: 500; color: #111827; }
  .cover-class {
    grid-column: span 2; margin-top: 16px; text-align: center;
    color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 5px;
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.2);
    background: rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.04);
    border-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* ============== Page ============== */
  .page {
    padding: 0 2mm;
    /* 不再 page-break-before always —— 让内容自然流，只在需要时手动 break */
  }
  .force-break { page-break-before: always; break-before: page; }

  /* TOC */
  .toc.page {
    /* 不再 min-height: 100vh — 与 box-sizing 在 chromium PDF 下会溢出 1mm 触发空白页 */
    box-sizing: border-box;
    padding: 12mm 12mm 14mm 12mm;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .toc h2 { text-align: center; letter-spacing: 16px; font-size: 30px; margin: 0 0 6mm 0; color: #1f2937; }
  .toc .toc-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; counter-reset: toc; max-width: 170mm; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 100%; }
  .toc .toc-list > li {
    counter-increment: toc;
    display: flex; align-items: baseline;
    padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px dotted #d1d5db;
    font-size: 15.5px;
  }
  .toc .toc-list > li::before {
    content: counter(toc) ".";
    color: #2563eb; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace;
    font-weight: 600; min-width: 32px; font-size: 16px;
  }
  .toc-title { flex: 1; }
  .toc-page { color: #6b7280; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace; font-size: 14px; }
  .toc-hint {
    margin: 4mm auto 0; max-width: 170mm; padding: 10px 14px;
    background: #f9fafb; border-left: 3px solid #2563eb;
    font-size: 12.5px; color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .toc-extra { max-width: 170mm; margin: 5mm auto 0; width: 100%; }
  .toc-block { margin-bottom: 5mm; }
  .toc-block-title {
    font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 6px; padding-left: 10px;
    border-left: 3px solid #722ed1;
  }
  .toc-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13.5px; }
  .toc-table td {
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }
  .toc-table td:first-child {
    width: 28%; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 500;
  }
  .toc-table td:last-child { color: #111827; }
  .toc-guide { margin: 0; padding-left: 22px; font-size: 13.5px; line-height: 1.8; color: #374151; }
  .toc-guide li { margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .toc-guide b { color: #2563eb; }
  .toc-footer {
    margin-top: auto; padding-top: 8px;
    border-top: 1px dashed #d1d5db;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 11.5px; color: #9ca3af;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
  }

  /* Section heading */
  h2.sec {
    font-size: 22px; font-weight: 600;
    margin: 18px 0 12px 0; padding-bottom: 7px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #2563eb;
    page-break-after: avoid;
    break-after: avoid;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  h2.sec:first-of-type { margin-top: 6px; }
  /* 防孤悬：h2 与紧随的 p / table / stat-row / fig 同组，整体推下页 */
  h2.sec + p,
  h2.sec + .stat-row,
  h2.sec + table.t,
  h2.sec + .fig,
  h2.sec + h3.subsec,
  h2.sec + ul,
  h2.sec + ol {
    page-break-before: avoid;
    break-before: avoid;
  }
  h3.subsec {
    font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600;
    margin: 16px 0 9px 0; padding-left: 11px;
    border-left: 4px solid #722ed1;
    page-break-after: avoid;
    break-after: avoid;
    color: #1f2937;
  }
  h3.subsec + table.t,
  h3.subsec + p,
  h3.subsec + .fig {
    page-break-before: avoid;
    break-before: avoid;
  }
  p { margin: 0 0 12px 0; text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.85; font-size: 14.5px; }
  p.no-indent { text-indent: 0; }
  ul, ol { margin: 6px 0 14px 0; padding-left: 26px; font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.9; }
  ul li, ol li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  b, strong { color: #111827; font-weight: 600; }

  /* Tables */
  table.t {
    width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 13.5px;
    margin: 8px 0 14px 0;
  }
  table.t thead th {
    background: #f3f4f6; color: #111827;
    text-align: left; padding: 9px 12px;
    border-top: 1px solid #d1d5db;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #2563eb;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  table.t tbody td {
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    vertical-align: top;
  }
  table.t tbody tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #fafafa; }
  table.t tr { page-break-inside: avoid; }
  td.num, th.num { text-align: right; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
  td.code { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace; font-size: 12.5px; word-break: break-all; }
  td.empty { text-align: center; color: #9ca3af; font-style: italic; padding: 16px; }

  .sev-pill { display: inline-block; padding: 2px 9px; border-radius: 3px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; }
  .sev-dot { display: inline-block; width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; margin-right: 7px; vertical-align: middle; }

  /* 2 列 layout (减少留白 -- 同章节 2 表/2 段并列) */
  .row2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 18px; margin: 8px 0 10px 0; }
  .row2 > * { min-width: 0; }
  .row2 h3.subsec:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; }
  /* 当 row2 内含 .fig 时，改单列让图表全宽（双栏图太小看不清字） */
  .row1 { display: block; margin: 8px 0 10px 0; }

  /* figure */
  .fig { margin: 10px 0 14px 0; page-break-inside: avoid; text-align: center; }
  .fig svg { max-width: 100%; height: auto; }
  .fig-cap { margin-top: 4px; font-size: 13px; color: #4b5563; letter-spacing: 1px; }

  .empty-block { color: #9ca3af; font-style: italic; padding: 12px 0; font-size: 14px; }

  /* 紧凑卡片 (用于把 stats 嵌进文本流) */
  .stat-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 10px;
    margin: 10px 0 14px 0;
  }
  .stat-row .cell {
    border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
    padding: 12px 14px; border-radius: 4px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fbfcfe 0%, #ffffff 100%);
  }
  .stat-row .cell-label { font-size: 13px; color: #6b7280; }
  .stat-row .cell-value {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", Consolas, monospace;
    font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #111827;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }
  .stat-row .cell.sev-c { border-left-color: #dc2626; }
  .stat-row .cell.sev-h { border-left-color: #ea580c; }
  .stat-row .cell.sev-m { border-left-color: #ca8a04; }
  .stat-row .cell.sev-l { border-left-color: #0891b2; }
  .stat-row .cell.brand { border-left-color: #722ed1; }
  .stat-row .cell.good { border-left-color: #22c55e; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ============== Cover (page 1) ============== -->
<section class="cover">
  <div class="cover-brand">
    {{if .Assets.LogoURI}}
    <img src="{{.Assets.LogoURI}}" alt="logo"/>
    {{end}}
    <div>
      <div class="cover-brand-name">矩阵云安全平台</div>
      <div class="cover-brand-en">MxCwpp Security Platform</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cover-mid">
    <div class="cover-kind">K8s 容器安全</div>
    <h1 class="cover-title">专项分析报告</h1>
    <div class="cover-period">{{.Meta.Period}}</div>
    <div class="cover-deco"></div>

    <div class="cover-highlights">
      <div class="hl"><div class="hl-num">{{.Summary.ClusterCount}}</div><div class="hl-lbl">纳管集群</div></div>
      <div class="hl hl-c"><div class="hl-num">{{.Summary.TotalAlarms}}</div><div class="hl-lbl">容器告警</div></div>
      <div class="hl hl-b"><div class="hl-num">{{.Summary.TotalWorkloads}}</div><div class="hl-lbl">工作负载</div></div>
      <div class="hl hl-p"><div class="hl-num">{{printf "%.1f" .Summary.BaselinePassRate}}%</div><div class="hl-lbl">基线通过率</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="cover-summary">
      <div class="cover-summary-title">本期摘要</div>
      <div class="cover-summary-text">
        平台纳管 <b>{{.Summary.ClusterCount}}</b> 个 K8s 集群（运行 {{.Summary.RunningClusters}} / 离线 {{.Summary.OfflineClusters}}），
        覆盖 <b>{{.Meta.TotalNodes}}</b> 个节点 · <b>{{.Meta.TotalPods}}</b> 个 Pod · <b>{{.Meta.TotalNs}}</b> 个 Namespace；
        本周期共产生容器安全告警 <b>{{.Summary.TotalAlarms}}</b> 条
        （待处理 {{.Summary.PendingAlarms}} / 已处理 {{.Summary.ProcessedAlarms}} / 已忽略 {{.Summary.IgnoredAlarms}}）；
        CIS 基线检查通过率 <b>{{printf "%.1f" .Summary.BaselinePassRate}}%</b>，集群平均健康度 <b>{{printf "%.1f" .Summary.AvgHealthScore}}</b>。
        告警量{{.Trend.Verb}} <b>{{printf "%.1f" .Trend.AbsPct}}%</b>，整体威胁态势<b>{{.Trend.Descriptor}}</b>。
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="cover-meta">
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">报告编号</span><span class="cover-meta-value">{{.Meta.ReportID}}</span></div>
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">生成时间</span><span class="cover-meta-value">{{.Meta.GeneratedAt}}</span></div>
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">报告周期</span><span class="cover-meta-value">{{.Meta.Period}}</span></div>
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">纳管集群</span><span class="cover-meta-value">{{.Meta.ClusterCount}} 个</span></div>
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">节点 / Pod</span><span class="cover-meta-value">{{.Meta.TotalNodes}} / {{.Meta.TotalPods}}</span></div>
    <div class="cover-meta-row"><span class="cover-meta-label">渲染引擎</span><span class="cover-meta-value">Gotenberg + Chromium</span></div>
    <div class="cover-class">机　密 · 仅 限 内 部 使 用</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============== TOC (page 2) ============== -->
<section class="page toc force-break">
  <h2>目　录</h2>
  <ol class="toc-list">
    <li><span class="toc-title">执行摘要 · 核心结论</span><span class="toc-page">03</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">关键指标概览</span><span class="toc-page">03</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">集群拓扑与健康度</span><span class="toc-page">04</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">CIS 基线检查与分类通过率</span><span class="toc-page">05</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">告警严重程度与类型分布</span><span class="toc-page">06</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">Top 工作负载与命名空间</span><span class="toc-page">07</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">镜像扫描与高危镜像</span><span class="toc-page">08</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">CVE 关联与漏洞分布</span><span class="toc-page">09</span></li>
    <li><span class="toc-title">改进建议与报告说明</span><span class="toc-page">10</span></li>
  </ol>
  <div class="toc-extra">
    <div class="toc-block">
      <div class="toc-block-title">数据范围</div>
      <table class="toc-table">
        <tr><td>报告周期</td><td>{{.Meta.Period}}</td></tr>
        <tr><td>集群覆盖</td><td>{{.Meta.ClusterCount}} 个集群 · {{.Meta.TotalNodes}} 节点 · {{.Meta.TotalPods}} Pod</td></tr>
        <tr><td>告警 / 基线</td><td>{{.Summary.TotalAlarms}} 条告警 · 基线通过率 {{printf "%.1f" .Summary.BaselinePassRate}}%</td></tr>
        <tr><td>镜像扫描</td><td>{{.Images.ScannedImages}} / {{.Images.TotalImages}} 已扫描 · 高危镜像 {{.Images.CriticalImgs}}</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div class="toc-footer">
      © 矩阵云安全 · MxCwpp Security Platform　|　报告引擎 v1.0　|　所有数据为实时观测，未经任何人工修饰
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============== §1 执行摘要 + §2 关键指标 (强制新页) ============== -->
<section class="page force-break">
  <h2 class="sec">1. 执行摘要</h2>
  <p>
    本报告覆盖 <b>{{.Meta.Period}}</b>，对接入矩阵云安全平台的 <b>{{.Summary.ClusterCount}}</b> 个 K8s 集群
    （运行 <b>{{.Summary.RunningClusters}}</b> / 离线 <b>{{.Summary.OfflineClusters}}</b>）
    共 <b>{{.Meta.TotalNodes}}</b> 个节点、<b>{{.Meta.TotalPods}}</b> 个 Pod、<b>{{.Meta.TotalNs}}</b> 个 Namespace 进行容器安全态势分析。
    报告期内共产生容器安全告警 <b>{{.Summary.TotalAlarms}}</b> 条
    （待处理 <b>{{.Summary.PendingAlarms}}</b> · 已处理 <b>{{.Summary.ProcessedAlarms}}</b> · 已忽略 <b>{{.Summary.IgnoredAlarms}}</b>），
    工作负载总数 <b>{{.Summary.TotalWorkloads}}</b>，CIS 基线检查通过率 <b>{{printf "%.1f" .Summary.BaselinePassRate}}%</b>，
    集群平均健康度 <b>{{printf "%.1f" .Summary.AvgHealthScore}}</b>。
    与上一周期对比，告警量{{.Trend.Verb}} <b>{{printf "%.1f" .Trend.AbsPct}}%</b>
    （{{.Trend.PrevTotal}} → {{.Summary.TotalAlarms}}），整体威胁态势<b>{{.Trend.Descriptor}}</b>。
  </p>

  <h3 class="subsec">核心结论</h3>
  <ul>
    {{range .Conclusions}}<li>{{.}}</li>{{end}}
  </ul>

  <h2 class="sec">2. 关键指标概览</h2>

  <div class="stat-row">
    <div class="cell good"><div class="cell-label">纳管集群</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.ClusterCount}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">运行 / 离线</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.RunningClusters}}<span style="font-size:11px;color:#6b7280"> / {{.Summary.OfflineClusters}}</span></div></div>
    <div class="cell brand"><div class="cell-label">告警总数</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.TotalAlarms}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-h"><div class="cell-label">待处理告警</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.PendingAlarms}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell"><div class="cell-label">工作负载</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Summary.TotalWorkloads}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell good"><div class="cell-label">基线通过率</div><div class="cell-value">{{printf "%.1f" .Summary.BaselinePassRate}}%</div></div>
    <div class="cell brand"><div class="cell-label">平均健康度</div><div class="cell-value">{{printf "%.1f" .Summary.AvgHealthScore}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-c"><div class="cell-label">环比变化</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Trend.Arrow}} {{printf "%.1f" .Trend.AbsPct}}%</div></div>
  </div>

  <table class="t">
    <thead><tr><th style="width:30%">指标</th><th style="width:25%" class="num">本周期</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>集群运行率</td><td class="num">{{.Summary.RunningClusters}} / {{.Summary.ClusterCount}}</td><td>运行中集群 / 纳管集群总数</td></tr>
      <tr><td>告警处理率</td><td class="num">{{.Summary.ProcessedAlarms}} / {{.Summary.TotalAlarms}}</td><td>已处理告警占比，反映安全运营响应能力</td></tr>
      <tr><td>基线通过率</td><td class="num">{{printf "%.1f" .Summary.BaselinePassRate}}%</td><td>CIS Kubernetes Benchmark 合规度</td></tr>
      <tr><td>镜像扫描覆盖率</td><td class="num">{{.Images.ScannedImages}} / {{.Images.TotalImages}}</td><td>已扫描镜像 / 平台收集镜像总数</td></tr>
      <tr><td>环比变化</td><td class="num">{{.Trend.Arrow}} {{printf "%.1f" .Trend.AbsPct}}%</td><td>vs 上一周期 {{.Trend.PrevTotal}} 条 · {{.Trend.Descriptor}}</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ============== §3 集群拓扑 (force break) ============== -->
<section class="page force-break">
  <h2 class="sec">3. 集群拓扑与健康度</h2>
  <p>
    本周期平台纳管 <b>{{.Summary.ClusterCount}}</b> 个 K8s 集群，覆盖 <b>{{.Meta.TotalNodes}}</b> 个节点、<b>{{.Meta.TotalPods}}</b> 个 Pod、<b>{{.Meta.TotalNs}}</b> 个 Namespace。
    集群健康度综合考虑组件运行状态、节点 Ready 比例、关键 Pod 异常重启次数、基线合规度等维度。
  </p>

  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:24px">#</th>
        <th>集群名称</th>
        <th style="width:90px">版本</th>
        <th style="width:80px">状态</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:60px">节点</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:60px">Pod</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:80px">Namespace</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:70px">健康度</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range $i, $c := .Clusters}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{add $i 1}}</td>
        <td>{{$c.Name}}</td>
        <td>{{$c.Version}}</td>
        <td><span class="sev-pill" style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.04);color:{{$c.StatusColor}}">{{$c.StatusLabel}}</span></td>
        <td class="num">{{$c.NodeCount}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{$c.PodCount}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{$c.NamespaceCount}}</td>
        <td class="num"><b>{{$c.HealthScore}}</b></td>
      </tr>
      {{else}}
      <tr><td class="empty" colspan="8">本周期未纳管 K8s 集群</td></tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ============== §4 基线检查 (force break) ============== -->
<section class="page force-break">
  <h2 class="sec">4. CIS 基线检查与分类通过率</h2>
  <p>
    本周期共执行 CIS Kubernetes Benchmark 基线检查 <b>{{.Baseline.Total}}</b> 项，
    通过 <b>{{.Baseline.Passed}}</b> 项 · 失败 <b>{{.Baseline.Failed}}</b> 项 · 警告 <b>{{.Baseline.Warning}}</b> 项，
    整体通过率 <b>{{printf "%.1f" .Baseline.PassRate}}%</b>。
  </p>

  <div class="stat-row">
    <div class="cell brand"><div class="cell-label">检查项总数</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Baseline.Total}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell good"><div class="cell-label">通过</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Baseline.Passed}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-c"><div class="cell-label">失败</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Baseline.Failed}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-m"><div class="cell-label">警告</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Baseline.Warning}}</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="row1">
    <div class="fig">
      {{.Charts.BaselineCatBar}}
      <div class="fig-cap">图 4-1　基线分类通过率（升序排列，最差排前）</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="subsec">4.1　分类通过率明细</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <thead><tr><th>类别</th><th class="num" style="width:80px">检查项</th><th class="num" style="width:80px">通过</th><th class="num" style="width:80px">失败</th><th class="num" style="width:100px">通过率</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range .Baseline.ByCategory}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{.Label}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{.Total}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{.Passed}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{.Failed}}</td>
        <td class="num"><b style="color:{{.RateColor}}">{{printf "%.1f" .PassRate}}%</b></td>
      </tr>
      {{else}}
      <tr><td class="empty" colspan="5">本周期无基线分类数据</td></tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="subsec">4.2　失败项严重程度分布</h3>
  <div class="row2">
    <div class="fig">
      {{.Charts.BaselineSevPie}}
      <div class="fig-cap">图 4-2　基线失败项严重程度分布</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <table class="t">
        <thead><tr><th>严重程度</th><th class="num" style="width:80px">数量</th><th class="num" style="width:80px">占比</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          {{range .Baseline.BySeverity}}
          <tr>
            <td><span class="sev-dot" style="background:{{.Color}}"></span>{{.Label}}</td>
            <td class="num">{{.Count}}</td>
            <td class="num">{{printf "%.1f" .Pct}}%</td>
          </tr>
          {{end}}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  {{if .Baseline.TopFailed}}
  <h3 class="subsec">4.3　Top 失败检查项</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:24px">#</th>
        <th style="width:80px">检查 ID</th>
        <th>检查项</th>
        <th style="width:100px">类别</th>
        <th style="width:60px">级别</th>
        <th style="width:110px">集群</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range $i, $f := .Baseline.TopFailed}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{add $i 1}}</td>
        <td class="code">{{$f.CheckID}}</td>
        <td>{{$f.CheckName}}</td>
        <td>{{$f.CategoryLbl}}</td>
        <td><span class="sev-pill" style="background:{{$f.BgColor}};color:{{$f.Color}}">{{$f.SevLabel}}</span></td>
        <td>{{$f.ClusterName}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
  {{end}}
</section>

<!-- ============== §5 告警分布 (force break) ============== -->
<section class="page force-break">
  <h2 class="sec">5. 告警严重程度与类型分布</h2>
  <p>告警按严重程度（critical / high / medium / low）与攻击类型维度统计，反映本周期容器安全主要威胁面。</p>

  <div class="fig">
    {{.Charts.SeverityPie}}
    <div class="fig-cap">图 5-1　容器告警严重程度分布</div>
  </div>

  <table class="t">
    <thead><tr><th>严重程度</th><th class="num" style="width:120px">数量</th><th class="num" style="width:120px">占比</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range .SeverityRows}}
      <tr>
        <td><span class="sev-dot" style="background:{{.Color}}"></span>{{.Label}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{.Count}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{printf "%.1f" .Pct}}%</td>
      </tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <div class="fig">
    {{.Charts.AlarmTypeBar}}
    <div class="fig-cap">图 5-2　Top 告警类型分布</div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="subsec">5.1　告警类型明细</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <thead><tr><th style="width:28px">#</th><th>告警类型</th><th class="num" style="width:100px">命中</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range $i, $t := .TopAlarmType}}
      <tr><td>{{add $i 1}}</td><td>{{$t.Label}}</td><td class="num">{{$t.Count}}</td></tr>
      {{else}}
      <tr><td class="empty" colspan="3">本周期无告警类型分布</td></tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ============== §6 Top 工作负载 + 命名空间 (force break) ============== -->
<section class="page force-break">
  <h2 class="sec">6. Top 工作负载与命名空间</h2>

  <h3 class="subsec">6.1　Top 受影响工作负载</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:24px">#</th>
        <th>工作负载</th>
        <th style="width:110px">Namespace</th>
        <th style="width:110px">集群</th>
        <th style="width:110px">告警类型</th>
        <th style="width:60px">级别</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:60px">告警</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range $i, $w := .TopWorkloads}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{add $i 1}}</td>
        <td>{{$w.Target}}</td>
        <td>{{$w.Namespace}}</td>
        <td>{{$w.ClusterName}}</td>
        <td>{{$w.AlarmLabel}}</td>
        <td><span class="sev-pill" style="background:{{$w.BgColor}};color:{{$w.Color}}">{{$w.SevLabel}}</span></td>
        <td class="num">{{$w.Count}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{else}}
      <tr><td class="empty" colspan="7">本周期无工作负载告警</td></tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="subsec">6.2　Top 命名空间分布</h3>
  <div class="row2">
    <div class="fig">
      {{.Charts.NamespaceBar}}
      <div class="fig-cap">图 6-1　Top 命名空间告警数</div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <table class="t">
        <thead><tr><th style="width:28px">#</th><th>Namespace</th><th style="width:90px">集群</th><th class="num" style="width:60px">告警</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          {{range $i, $n := .TopNamespace}}
          <tr><td>{{add $i 1}}</td><td>{{$n.Namespace}}</td><td>{{$n.ClusterName}}</td><td class="num">{{$n.Count}}</td></tr>
          {{else}}
          <tr><td class="empty" colspan="4">本周期无命名空间分布</td></tr>
          {{end}}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ============== §7 镜像扫描 (force break) ============== -->
<section class="page force-break">
  <h2 class="sec">7. 镜像扫描与高危镜像</h2>
  <p>
    本周期共收集镜像 <b>{{.Images.TotalImages}}</b> 个，已扫描 <b>{{.Images.ScannedImages}}</b> 个，
    含漏洞镜像 <b>{{.Images.VulnerableImgs}}</b> 个，其中含严重 CVE 的镜像 <b>{{.Images.CriticalImgs}}</b> 个、
    高危镜像 <b>{{.Images.HighRiskImgs}}</b> 个。
  </p>

  <div class="stat-row">
    <div class="cell brand"><div class="cell-label">镜像总数</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Images.TotalImages}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell good"><div class="cell-label">已扫描</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Images.ScannedImages}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-h"><div class="cell-label">含漏洞</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Images.VulnerableImgs}}</div></div>
    <div class="cell sev-c"><div class="cell-label">严重 CVE</div><div class="cell-value">{{.Images.CriticalImgs}}</div></div>
  </div>

  <h3 class="subsec">7.1　Top 高风险镜像</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:24px">#</th>
        <th>镜像</th>
        <th style="width:120px">OS</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:80px">漏洞总数</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:80px">严重</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:80px">高危</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range $i, $img := .Images.TopRisky}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{add $i 1}}</td>
        <td class="code">{{$img.Image}}</td>
        <td>{{$img.OS}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{$img.TotalVulns}}</td>
        <td class="num"><b style="color:#dc2626">{{$img.CriticalCnt}}</b></td>
        <td class="num"><b style="color:#ea580c">{{$img.HighCnt}}</b></td>
      </tr>
      {{else}}
      <tr><td class="empty" colspan="6">本周期无高风险镜像</td></tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ============== §8 CVE 关联 (force break) ============== -->
<section class="page force-break">
  <h2 class="sec">8. CVE 关联与漏洞分布</h2>
  <p>本周期镜像扫描关联的 Top CVE 漏洞，按命中镜像数排序，反映平台主要暴露的已知漏洞面。</p>

  <table class="t">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th style="width:24px">#</th>
        <th style="width:140px">CVE ID</th>
        <th style="width:70px">级别</th>
        <th>标题</th>
        <th class="num" style="width:80px">命中</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {{range $i, $c := .TopCVEs}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{add $i 1}}</td>
        <td class="code">{{$c.CveID}}</td>
        <td><span class="sev-pill" style="background:{{$c.BgColor}};color:{{$c.Color}}">{{$c.SevLabel}}</span></td>
        <td>{{$c.Title}}</td>
        <td class="num">{{$c.Count}}</td>
      </tr>
      {{else}}
      <tr><td class="empty" colspan="5">本周期无 CVE 关联数据</td></tr>
      {{end}}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

<!-- ============== §9 改进建议 + 附录 (force break) ============== -->
<section class="page force-break">
  <h2 class="sec">9. 改进建议</h2>
  <p>基于本周期数据，平台自动生成如下改进建议供安全团队参考：</p>
  <ol>
    {{range .Improvements}}<li>{{.}}</li>{{else}}<li>本周期未生成自动建议（数据样本较小或检测充分）。</li>{{end}}
  </ol>

  <h3 class="subsec">附录 A　报告说明</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <tbody>
      <tr><td style="width:30%">数据来源</td><td>MySQL（kube_clusters / kube_alarms / kube_baseline_results / kube_images / kube_cves 等元数据） + ClickHouse（容器实时遥测）</td></tr>
      <tr><td>生成方式</td><td>矩阵云安全平台服务端 Go html/template 渲染，自动生成无人工调整</td></tr>
      <tr><td>图表渲染</td><td>服务端 SVG 手绘，矢量化、可缩放、PDF 中保持清晰</td></tr>
      <tr><td>PDF 引擎</td><td>Chromium Headless（Gotenberg HTML→PDF），文本可搜索、可复制、可粘贴</td></tr>
      <tr><td>报告编号</td><td>{{.Meta.ReportID}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>生成时间</td><td>{{.Meta.GeneratedAt}}</td></tr>
      <tr><td>密级</td><td>机密 · 仅限内部使用 · 不得转发至非授权人员</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h3 class="subsec">附录 B　术语对照</h3>
  <table class="t">
    <thead><tr><th style="width:25%">术语</th><th>定义</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td>CIS Benchmark</td><td>Center for Internet Security 安全配置基线，K8s 维度涵盖 RBAC / 网络策略 / Pod 安全等</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Workload</td><td>K8s 工作负载，包含 Deployment / StatefulSet / DaemonSet / Job 等</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Namespace</td><td>K8s 命名空间，资源隔离边界</td></tr>
      <tr><td>容器逃逸</td><td>攻击者突破容器隔离边界，从容器内访问宿主机资源的行为</td></tr>
      <tr><td>CVE</td><td>Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures 通用漏洞披露，业界标准漏洞编号</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</section>

</body>
</html>
